notes.text: We now ensure that UI5 tooling supports the changes made to the manifest file in the adaptation projects
We now support AI-Assisted error resolution feature in the object pages for a beta release
We now support the handling of 503 error responses
We've resolved an issue with the visibility of the Paste button on tables in the object pages
We now ensure that navigation works correctly when the Edm.DateTime fields are present in an object page
We've resolved an issue with adding more filters from the Adapt Filters dialog in the analytical list page applications
We've now added an invisible text as the label for the multi-view dropdown menu in the single table mode for accessibility
We now ensure that side effects work properly when fields with intent-based links are present on the object pages
